Source:
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  ID: 50ae0a98-5702-40cb-8c11-4c6297aa457a
  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 14
  Paragraph: 36
Title: The Turning Of Heaven
---
When Confucius returned from his visit with Lao Tan, he did not speak
for three days. His disciples said, "Master, you've seen Lao Tan - what
estimation would you make of him?"
